        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Literature research. According to 'Front Research' the global production volume of trisodium phosphate in 2014 was more than 800 000 tonnes. It is assumed here assumed that the global production volume is 800 000 tonnes. 

Reference:
Front Research, Trisodium phosphate (TSP) Global Market and Forecast Research. Retrieved from: http://www.frontresearch.com/reports/additives/trisodium-phosphate-tsp-global-market-and-forecast-research/ on 15 of July 2017.</productionVolumeComment>
