      <intermediateExchange id="b3993592-0486-5db4-9844-def15a556235" unitId="487df68b-4994-4027-8fdc-a4dc298257b7" casNumber="007664-38-2" amount="0.632370122573252" intermediateExchangeId="f4feb7e2-19a8-40af-84e0-9cd7c7142777" activityLinkId="a8667e14-192e-5442-9134-f9642500cdda">
        <name xml:lang="en">phosphoric acid, industrial grade, without water, in 85% solution state</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Calculated value based on stoichiometric calculations and literature data. 
97.995182g/mol is the molar mass of phosphoric acid, industrial grade, without water, in 85% solution state (H3O4P). 
163.940666g/mol is the molar mass of trisodium phosphate (Na3O4P). 

Trisodium phosphate is modelled here as the product of the reaction of phosphoric acid with sodium hydroxide (Schrödter 2008).
Chemical reaction:
3NaOH + H3PO4 -&gt; Na3PO4 + 3 H2O
Sodium hydroxide can be substituted with NaOCl, NaCL, NaNO3 (Schrödter 2008).</comment>
